title: Plane Crazy / All the Way Boys (1972) Jungle Adventure - with Terence Hill & Bud Spencer

sources.title: Plane Crazy / All the Way Boys (1972) Jungle Adventure - with Terence Hill & Bud Spencer
sources.description:
Those "TRINITY BOYS" take to the air and still fly off the handle!
Plata and Salud crash-land their insurance scam in the Amazon, stumbling onto Mr. Ears’ diamond mine where fists fly faster than their rickety planes. Now they’re dodging his goons, brewing chaos, and proving even sky-high cons can’t outrun a jungle brawl.

Plane Crazy / All the Way Boys (1972) 
Original title: ...Più forte ragazzi!

Director: Giuseppe Colizzi
Writers: Giuseppe Colizzi, Barbara Alberti, Amedeo Pagani

Main cast:
Terence Hill - Plata
Bud Spencer - Salud
Reinhard Kolldehoff - Mr. Ears
Cyril Cusack - Matto
Riccardo Pizzuti - Naso
Carlos Muñoz - Augusto

Genres: Action, Comedy, Jungle Adventure, Slapstick
Release date: December 22, 1972 (Italy)
Filming location: Colombia
